    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that's ready to work? This car is in honest, fair condition and is perfect for someone who values performance over perfection! While the exterior shows some character with typical wear and the interior has been well-loved, it remains a dependable ride that gets the job done. It's a solid, functional vehicle at a great price point for anyone looking for a practical and trustworthy set of wheels!",
