    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major electronic components are fully functional. While the exterior shows some minor road wear and light surface scratches consistent with its age, the interior remains clean and free of major blemishes. It is a reliable daily driver that provides a comfortable ride and requires no immediate repairs.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several large dents, significant paint fading, and some rust spots on the rocker panels. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places, and there is a persistent musty odor. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears; it also has a persistent oil leak and needs immediate brake work. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, and I strongly recommend a professional inspection before purchase.",
      "price": 4500.0,
